description: Passengers describe hearing a "massive bang" and seeing a "bright flash" at the time of the strike.
title: Flybe plane travelling to Jersey hit by lightning
title_page: Flybe plane travelling to Jersey hit by lightning - BBC News
maintext: "Flybe's engineers have since confirmed that the aircraft sustained no damage during the incident," the spokesman said, adding that arrangements had been made to allow passengers to continue their journeys.
